												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Karlach shrugs, amused at Henk's horribleness. She reaches for the drink to hold it aloft and propose a toast, but she fumbles it and knocks the glass over, then she back to standard sitting pose. Please reach out to Greg for staging/characters/props placaments ref [CHOICES]"
