			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Gortash must have been permadefeated and Karlach has to be in the party and have an avatar romantic partner and move to CTY_Main_A. Then go a long rest. More than one might be needed specially since Orin's abduction has priority over this night.\r\nIf using the origin debug book then:\r\n1. Load CTY_Main_A\r\n2. Recruit Karlach as a companion.\r\n3. \"Karlach\" -> \"Act 3 Romance\" -> \"Partner Karlach\"\r\n3. \"Karlach\" -> \"Act 3 Romance\" -> \"Unlock romance night\""
				},
